<tr id="L358"><td><a href="#L358">358</a></td><td>ARCHER:  Go to hell.</td></tr>

<tr id="L359"><td><a href="#L359">359</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: Tolaris pushes him away, against the wall, then lifts him off his feet against the ceiling and throws him over the desk. Archer removes a phase pistol from the back of his chair.</td></tr>

